01:19:35.000 --> 01:19:37.790 align:middle line:84%
and then we'll do
analysis in R2 and we'll

01:19:37.790 --> 01:19:42.470 align:middle line:84%
prove theorem one prime
and theorem two prime.

01:19:42.470 --> 01:19:43.710 align:middle line:90%
OK, great.

01:19:43.710 --> 01:19:44.550 align:middle line:90%
Let's stop there.

